name: From VHS: An incredible story
description: This is the incredible story of how X (8yo) and her brother Y (13yo)  while playing at “Catch me if you can” found these old hologram of ancient church organ tubes inside a tree trunk on their way back home after school in the Russian part of the Boreal Forest. It dates from 2022. | An original artwork by Iskra Velitchkova. GIF.
